## Quick Start

### Prerequisites

- Go 1.23+
- Node.js 18+
- Make

### Setup

```bash
# Install dependencies
make setup

# Start development server
make dev
```

Open [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080) in your browser.

## Development

### Available Commands

```bash
make dev              # Start all watchers (air + templ + tailwind)
make build            # Build for production
make test             # Run tests
make setup            # Install dependencies
make clean            # Clean build artifacts
```

### Individual Watchers

```bash
make watch-air        # Go hot reload
make watch-templ      # templ file watcher
make watch-tailwind   # Tailwind CSS watcher
```

### Code Generation

```bash
make templ-generate   # Generate templ code
{{- if ne .Database "none"}}
make sqlc-generate    # Generate sqlc code
{{- end}}
```

